---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="Sobre Nosotros · Ingeniería orientada a producción"
  descripcion="Conoce al equipo de LRA Cloud Operations. Ingenieros DevOps especializados en AWS, Kubernetes, Terraform y Platform Engineering con más de 4 años de experiencia en producción."
>

  <!-- ─── HERO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147,184,255,0.18) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 110%, rgba(30,111,255,0.18) 0%, transparent 65%);"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6 py-20 sm:py-28 text-center">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6" style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.2); color: #93b8ff; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.25);">
        Sobre nosotros
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
        Ingeniería orientada a producción
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">
        Somos un equipo de 3 ingenieros DevOps que desarrollamos plataformas cloud-native aplicando prácticas modernas de Platform Engineering, automatización de infraestructura, Kubernetes, observabilidad y despliegues continuos sobre AWS y Azure.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.6);">
        3 ingenieros · AWS · Azure · Kubernetes · Platform Engineering · DevOps · Cybersecurity
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── NUESTRO EQUIPO ───────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">

      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;">
          Equipo
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #0A2540;">Nuestro equipo</h2>
        <p class="text-base max-w-xl mx-auto" style="color: #64748b;">
          3 ingenieros DevOps especializados en AWS, Kubernetes y Platform Engineering
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-10">

        <!-- ── LIQUENSON RUBEN ── -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10" style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(10,37,64,0.10); border-radius: 16px;">

          <div class="flex justify-center sm:justify-start mb-6">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full" style="background: #f0fdf4; color: #15803d; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 flex-shrink-0 animate-pulse"></span>
              Disponible para proyectos
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <img src="/images/profile.jpg" alt="Liquenson Ruben" class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full object-cover" style="border: 3px solid #c3d9ff;" />
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1" style="color: #0A2540;">Liquenson Ruben</h3>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    Las Palmas de Gran Canaria, Canarias, España
                  </div>
                </div>
                <a
                  href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/liquenson-ruben-490961269/"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl flex-shrink-0 transition-all hover:opacity-90 hover:scale-[1.02]"
                  style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A66C2 0%, #004182 100%); box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(10,102,194,0.3);"
                >
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
                  </svg>
                  LinkedIn
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 opacity-70" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
                {['DevOps Engineer', 'Platform Engineer', 'Cloud Engineer', 'Linux SysAdmin'].map(role => (
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;">
                    {role}
                  </span>
                ))}
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: #64748b;">
                Ingeniero DevOps con más de 4 años especializado en el diseño, despliegue y mantenimiento de infraestructuras cloud escalables y altamente disponibles. Amplio conocimiento en prácticas DevOps, automatización de CI/CD y arquitecturas basadas en AWS y contenedores. Experiencia sólida en IaC con Terraform y Ansible, orquestación con Kubernetes y ECS Fargate, y pipelines CI/CD con Jenkins, GitHub Actions y ArgoCD. Dominio de servicios clave de AWS y automatización con Bash, Shell y Python.
              </p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl inline-flex w-fit" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #0A2540; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;">
                <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #1E6FFF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                Disponible · Presencial y Remoto · Las Palmas de Gran Canaria
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ── DARWIN POCHET ── -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10" style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(10,37,64,0.10); border-radius: 16px;">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold text-white select-none" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E6FFF 0%, #0A2540 100%); border: 3px solid #c3d9ff;">
                DP
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1" style="color: #0A2540;">Darwin Pochet</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1" style="color: #1E6FFF;">CEO & IT Consultant</p>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    Raleigh, Carolina del Norte, Estados Unidos
                  </div>
                </div>
                <a
                  href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/darwin-pochet-156aa295/"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl flex-shrink-0 transition-all hover:opacity-90 hover:scale-[1.02]"
                  style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A66C2 0%, #004182 100%); box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(10,102,194,0.3);"
                >
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
                  </svg>
                  LinkedIn
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 opacity-70" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
                {['CEO', 'IT Consultant', 'Network Admin', 'Cybersecurity'].map(role => (
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;">
                    {role}
                  </span>
                ))}
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5" style="color: #64748b;">
                Fundador de Nibble Tech LLC con más de 20 años de experiencia en IT. Especializado en infraestructura de red, ciberseguridad, administración de sistemas Windows/Linux y soluciones IT para pequeñas y medianas empresas. Entusiasta de la IA aplicada a networking y automatización.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mb-5 pb-5 border-b border-gray-100">
                {['Linux', 'Firewalls', 'Windows Server', 'Cisco', 'Active Directory', 'Python', 'JavaScript', 'Node.js', 'Fortinet'].map(tag => (
                  <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full" style="background: #f8fafc; color: #64748b; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">{tag}</span>
                ))}
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                {['Fortinet Certified Associate Cybersecurity', 'Fortinet Certified Fundamentals Cybersecurity'].map(cert => (
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #0A2540; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;">
                    <svg class="w-3 h-3 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #1E6FFF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
                    </svg>
                    {cert}
                  </span>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ── KELVIN OSAIGBOVO ── -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10" style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(10,37,64,0.10); border-radius: 16px;">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold text-white select-none" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2540 0%, #1E3A6E 100%); border: 3px solid #c3d9ff;">
                KO
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-1" style="color: #0A2540;">Kelvin Osaigbovo</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold mb-1" style="color: #1E6FFF;">DevOps Engineer | Platform Engineer</p>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                    </svg>
                    Las Palmas de Gran Canaria, Canarias, España
                  </div>
                </div>
                <a
                  href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kelvin-osaigbovo/"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl flex-shrink-0 transition-all hover:opacity-90 hover:scale-[1.02]"
                  style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A66C2 0%, #004182 100%); box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(10,102,194,0.3);"
                >
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
                  </svg>
                  LinkedIn
                  <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 opacity-70" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
                {['DevOps Engineer', 'Platform Engineer', 'Cloud Engineer', 'Azure Admin'].map(role => (
                  <span class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;">
                    {role}
                  </span>
                ))}
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-5" style="color: #64748b;">
                Ingeniero DevOps con más de 4 años de experiencia construyendo y manteniendo entornos cloud. Especializado en CI/CD, AWS, Azure, Kubernetes y ECS Fargate. Actualmente Developer II - DevOps Engineering en UST España & Latam.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mb-5 pb-5 border-b border-gray-100">
                {['AWS', 'Azure', 'Kubernetes', 'Docker', 'Terraform', 'Ansible', 'Jenkins', 'ECS Fargate', 'Python', 'Bash', 'Git'].map(tag => (
                  <span class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full" style="background: #f8fafc; color: #64748b; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">{tag}</span>
                ))}
              </div>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full" style="background: #f0fdf4; color: #15803d; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;">
                  <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                  Developer II · UST España & Latam · jun 2025 – actualidad
                </span>
                <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #0A2540; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #1E6FFF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
                  </svg>
                  Cisco Introduction to Cybersecurity
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── EXPERIENCIA ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section style="background-color: #EEF4FF;" class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">

      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4" style="background: white; color: #1E6FFF; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;">
          Trayectoria profesional
        </span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #0A2540;">Experiencia</h2>
        <p class="text-base max-w-xl mx-auto" style="color: #64748b;">
          Entornos reales de producción. Infraestructura que funciona bajo presión.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Timeline -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Vertical line -->
        <div class="absolute left-6 sm:left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-px" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1E6FFF 0%, #c3d9ff 100%);"></div>

        <div class="space-y-10">

          <!-- iCareMedical -->
          <div class="relative flex gap-6 sm:gap-10">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 sm:w-16 flex justify-center">
              <div class="relative mt-1">
                <div class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-2 border-white z-10 relative" style="background: #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(30,111,255,0.2);"></div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex-1 pb-2">
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8" style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(10,37,64,0.07); border-radius: 16px;">
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">iCareMedical</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold mt-0.5" style="color: #1E6FFF;">DevOps Engineer</p>
                    <p class="text-xs mt-0.5 flex items-center gap-1" style="color: #64748b;">
                      <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
                      </svg>
                      Pearland, Texas · En remoto
                    </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex flex-col items-start sm:items-end gap-1.5">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                      <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 flex-shrink-0"></span>
                      <span class="text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full whitespace-nowrap" style="background: #f0fdf4; color: #15803d; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;">mayo 2022 – presente</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full" style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;">4 años 1 mes</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <ul class="space-y-2.5">
                  {[
                    'Diseñé e implementé pipelines CI/CD completos en AWS con Jenkins, Maven y SonarQube.',
                    'Infraestructura multi-AZ con Terraform cubriendo VPC, EC2, S3, CloudFront, RDS, Route 53 y CloudWatch.',
                    'Orquestación de contenedores con Kubernetes y Helm en producción.',
                    'Automatización con Ansible para gestión de configuración y aprovisionamiento de servidores.',
                    'Monitoreo y observabilidad con Prometheus y Grafana.',
                  ].map(bullet => (
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #64748b;">
